      • getModelPreviouslyAnnotated

        public static boolean getModelPreviouslyAnnotated(SemSimModel semsimmodel,
                                                  JSimProjectAccessor ma,
                                                  SemSimLibrary sslib)
        This method collects all annotations for an MML model using the RDF block associated with it in its parent project file. The method returns whether the model already contains SemSim annotations.
        Parameters:
        semsimmodel - The SemSim model to annotate, if annotations already exist in the JSim model
        ma - Location of the JSim model
        sslib - A SemSimLibrary instance
        Returns:
        Whether the JSim model already contains SemSim annotations.
